{"tid":2363906,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美國國會辦公室驚現《中國日報》（China Daily）","createTime":"2021-01-12T14:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T04:40:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bdd8a3c328b1cc50599548373023b6ca6f7ae65","tid":2363906,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"美國艾奧瓦州聯邦眾議員欣森（Ashley Hinson）日前致函眾議院議長佩洛西，要求對方解釋為何中國官方英文報紙《中國日報》（China Daily）會出現在國會辦公室中，並促請在國會禁絕中共刊物。<br />\n<br />\n欣森上周五（8日）致函佩洛西，指雖然她或其職員沒有提出要求，但當日早上卻在國會辦公室收到一份《中國日報》，對事件感到驚嚇，直指「這份危險的宣傳物是由中共擁有、資助和撰寫」。<br />\n<br />\n欣森要求佩洛西運用作為眾議院議長的控制權，阻止中共的出版物出現在美國國會，更稱這種「令人討厭的垃圾」不應花費公帑自動地在國會辦公室分發，形容此舉違背納稅人的信任。《中國日報》的總部設於北京，由中共中央宣傳部主辦，在美國已登記為外國代理人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210112/bkn-20210112174655691-0112_00992_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210112%2Fbkn-20210112174655691-0112_00992_001.html&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJubV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=3a2942f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210112/bkn-20210112174655691-0112_00992_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aa3dfa3487c47dfe34a8214f82996d5bb256651a","tid":2363906,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f96340b1fb71f9e2b5ab6deb5e537194b88ce89","tid":2363906,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7kL9-IIO4MBxHKqnSfuDDJM5foQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.ima